text: Unexpectedly Yours is a 2017 Filipino romantic comedy movie directed by Cathy Garcia-Molina and starring Sharon Cuneta, Robin Padilla, Julia Barretto, Joshua Garcia, Yayo Aguila. It was distributed by Star Cinema. ==Other websites== * Category:2017 romantic comedy movies Category:Filipino movies Category:Movies directed by Cathy Garcia-Molina
